	abstractNote = {Quantum communication has seen rapid progress towards
	                practical large-scale networks, with quantum key distribution
	                (QKD) spearheading this development. While fibre-based systems
	                have been shown to be well suited for metropolitan scales,
	                suitable fibre infrastructure may not always be in place. Here,
	                we make the case for an entanglement-based free-space quantum
